---
source: tests/cli_json.rs
expression: stdout
---
Show metadata for a public GigaFile page without downloading files

Usage: rgfile info [OPTIONS] <URL>

Arguments:
  <URL>  Download page URL

Options:
      --timeout <TIMEOUT>        Per-request timeout in seconds [default: 60]
  -v, --verbose...               Increase logging verbosity (-v for info, -vv for debug)
      --retries <RETRIES>        Retry count for retryable network/server failures [default: 3]
      --user-agent <USER_AGENT>  Override the default User-Agent
      --dump-page <DUMP_PAGE>    Save the fetched download page HTML for diagnostics
      --json                     Print one JSON object
  -q, --quiet                    Disable non-error status output
  -h, --help                     Print help
